description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions


Kate and Leisha discuss their dueling haircuts, give advice, and answer your questions on: if they believe in the supernatural, revisiting past questions, how they got their pets, what other projects they'd like to work on together, being an adult, holiday traditions, and how not to care what other people think.


Get Tickets To Their Live Show:

https://www.events.loopedlive.com/pants


Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram @ThePantsPod

Email us: pantspodcast@yahoo.com

Music: Carol Parra @csssuxxx
